Product: critic

critic is distributed under the terms of the standard BSD open source license.

Author:  The art Team   artists@fnal.gov

Description:

critic is used to test art and art related things such as gallery.
It is used for integration testing. It was initially created to test
the compatibility of art and gallery, although it may be extended
to include other tests in the future.

https://cdcvs.fnal.gov/redmine/projects/critic/wiki

art is an event-processing framework for particle physics experiments. 
Experiments use the art framework to build programs that process data 
in a variety of contexts.

https://cdcvs.fnal.gov/redmine/projects/art/wiki
